# L1-EXIT-010 / L2-RDR-021 empty-recording fixture.
#
# A valid but EMPTY recording: the record stream opens directly on the
# end-of-records terminator (a null Type Word, 0x0000). This is literally
# what a DDC recorder writes for an unused MIL-STD-1553 channel that
# captured no bus traffic. The decoder must treat it as a successful,
# empty decode — header-only CSV, exit 0 — NOT the exit-2 "wrong file"
# NoValidRecords rejection.

0000
